Imp Note : if we need to display any variable value , that variable should be precedded with $

Two types of variables in shell scripting
1) System defined variables (envrionmental variables or default variables) 
 echo $HOSTNAME or echo $USER or echo $PWD or echo $SHELL or  env | grep shell
2) Programmer defined variables (user varibles)   

