Ask the user for their age.
If age is greater than or equal to 18, print ‚ÄúEligible to vote‚Äù,
else print ‚ÄúNot eligible‚Äù.

#!/bin/bash
read -p " please enter the age of the user : " age

if [ $age -ge 18 ] ; then
echo "Your are eligible to vote"
else
echo "You are not eligible to vote"
fi

Ask the user for two subject marks: maths and science.
If both marks ‚â• 35, print ‚ÄúPass‚Äù, else ‚ÄúFail‚Äù.

#!/bin/bash
